race.comment: FLYING PROUD (1) is a strong stayer who excels over the longer races. Was sixth last time (38.44) over 660m at Bendigo in a Grade 4/5. Form at the trip excellent including three wins. Won at her only start from this draw. Can bounce back. ASTON PRATT (6) box seated before sticking on well to finish 1.5 lengths away in third (34.72) at this track in a Grade 4/5 over 600m. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings four times from seven starts. Expected to feature. MAGIC SCOTCH (4) was well back throughout but attacked the line to hit the frame when a 1.3 lengths second (30.36) at this track in Grade 5. Can measure up. REIKO DUSTY (2) was out of the money at this circuit last start but can bounce back.
